contentEn: >-
  The website for the magazine "ADAC Urlaub" underwent a design update in 2024.
  Using the CMS system, the website was completely redesigned from scratch so
  that users can see what this issue is about. It provides a preview of other
  topics and offers the option to order the magazine free of charge.
